    • Method Detail

      • run

        public void run()
        H263Packetizer's own scheme of packetizing video data.

        Workflow:

        1. Reads and skips bytes from input until it encounters the byte sequence "mdat"
        2. While the thread is running:
          • Fills buffer with bytes read from input
          • Scans the buffer for start code 00 00 1X
          • According to search result, sends the frame in single of multiple packets
        See Also:
        RFC 4629 Section 5.1 for the RTP payload header format of H.263 video.
